title: 92Noon on a Vikings GameDay
description: Early montage and Vikings/NFL talkers. Gophers coach PJ Fleck makes his weekly appearance during the first hour this time around. A cameo from Sinykin and more Vikings throughout the rest of the show, including Lavelle for most of the final hour. JG on the Gophers to wrap a gameday show!
